                                                                                                                                   Student hit

              
	Jalandhar, Jan. 15 (PTI): A student was mercilessly beaten by his teacher, who banged the boys head on the wall for switching on a fan in the classroom, his parents alleged. 
    
	Sagar Chabra, 15, a Class IX student of Greatway Co-education High School, sustained injuries on his arms, forehead and back. He was admitted to a hospital after being beaten yesterday by Vipin Bahal, police said. 
    
	Bahal was booked on the complaint of Sagars parents. 
                                                                                
